SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct b.contact_id, b.contact_first_name, b.contact_last_name, b.contact_organization_name, b.contact_email_address, b.Business_Email From contact b Where b.contact_parent_id = :1 :2 :3 AND b.contact_first_name<>'' AND b.contact_last_name<>'' AND b.contact_last_name<>b.contact_email_address Order by b.contact_organization_name, b.contact_last_name
select COUNT(DISTINCT b.contact_id) From contact b Where b.contact_parent_id = :1 :2 :3 AND b.contact_first_name<>'' AND b.contact_last_name<>'' AND b.contact_last_name<>b.contact_email_address

select distinct (b.event_id), b.title, b.start_date, b.end_date from contact a, calendar_schedule b where a.contact_id = b.operator_id AND b.publish='Y' AND a.contact_parent_id = :1 :2 :3 Order by b.title, b.start_date
select COUNT(DISTINCT b.event_id) from contact a, calendar_schedule b where a.contact_id = b.operator_id AND b.publish='Y' AND a.contact_parent_id = :1 :2 :3
SELECT ads_id, title, date_from FROM classified_ads WHERE site_owner=:1 AND city_dir=:2 :3 :4 ORDER BY date_from DESC, time_from DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM classified_ads WHERE site_owner=:1 AND city_dir=:2 :3 :4
